<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dinner Ordering</title>
    <style>
body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #000000;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 1em;
        }

        .menu-item {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 1em;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .menu-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .cart {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 1em;
            position: fixed;
            right: 1em;
            top: 1em;
            max-width: 300px;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #8eb50b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Dinner Menu</h1>
    </header>

    <section id="menu">
        <!-- Menu items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
    </section>

    <div class="cart" id="cart">
        <h2>Shopping Cart</h2>
        <div id="cart-items">
            <!-- Cart items will be dynamically added here using JavaScript -->
        </div>
        <p>Total: &#8377<span id="total">0.00</span></p>
        <button onclick="checkout()">Checkout</button>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Dinner Ordering</p>
    </footer>
